      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STORMY VISTA NZ (4) has won standing start races the last two times he has raced here. Led and kept going when he scored by more than 10 metres at this circuit and distance last start. Goes back 20m in the handicap but is racing well enough to win a race of this calibre. OUR VINNIE (10) did a good job to come from the 40m mark and finish runner-up at his most recent outing, beaten a head, in a nice return to form at Northam. Starts 10m closer in the handicap so could go one better. ARTFUL MAJOR (5) switches from the mobile start but is looming as a threat after a good effort last start, finishing second at this venue. CHIVALRY NZ (11) cops a 40m handicap but came from 10m further back for second at this venue the last time he attempted a standing start.",
